Thanx, Orchid!

::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe walks through the forest. He had carefully avoided grassy areas, 
and had stayed in the woods, where it was easier to hide. Any animals he had 
encoundered so far had all run away with one look at his hideous form. He 
continues on his way, going no where in particular.
